cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about language generation using recurrent neural networks and generative adversarial networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning and neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves training the model from scratch, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper compares its results with a convolutional baseline, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
